{"tid":1508101,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一定要救人！！一定要救人！！一定要救人呀大家！！","createTime":"2019-08-26T12:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:11:19.000Z","uid":115452,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"39a71544370809d0d2d09943163223d62aaf8d8e","tid":1508101,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"真勇武捉一個少一個<br />\n唔想呢場運動輸，唔割蓆係基本<br />\n但最重要係要救人呀！！<br />\n見到勇武比人捉唔該大叫<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊救</span></span></strong><br />\n大家比啲勇氣一齊上前<br />\n一個人好驚，叫多幾個就唔驚！<br />\n你救一個勇武可能救左呢場運動。<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家真係要有救人嘅行為。"},{"pid":"6d910ecfdc980a569a30a67a95cfc757a85a16ee","tid":1508101,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=fbfa0966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsWyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=3ffdb6f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/10245867655